name: Semwanti Vesh
description:
A 1/2 piece from the collection of characters in the upcoming graphic novel series, Veil Of The Gods. 


Semwanti Vesh is a Mahjeena, high level practitioner of the Mahjuti Technology. Her skill is such that she has learned to bend the Reality Mesh to her will. However, like Jatta Eye, she has become aware that something is wrong, something is out of balance, something sinister is at play, and whatever it is, it threatens the lives of everyone who inhabits the Mesh.
